"title": "8422: equipping, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8422: equipping, spiritual",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture provides examples of individuals who have been equipped to carry out tasks or responsibilities of a spiritual nature.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ was equipped for his work</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:2\">ISA 61:1–61:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:1\">PSA 72:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:4-Isa50:7\">ISA 50:4–50:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:18\">MAT 12:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1\">ISA 42:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18-Luke4:19\">LUK 4:18–4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:31\">LUK 19:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:34\">JHN 3:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:5\">HEB 10:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's people are equipped for service</h2>\n<h3>In the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:10-Exod4:12\">EXO 4:10–4:12</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:1-Exod31:6\">EXO 31:1–31:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:30-Exod36:2\">EXO 35:30–36:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:7-Lev8:9\">LEV 8:7–8:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">JDG 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:14\">JDG 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:34\">JDG 6:34</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:29\">JDG 11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:19\">JDG 14:19</a> <em>Samson</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:10\">1SA 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:7-1Kgs3:9\">1KI 3:7–3:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:12\">2CH 2:12</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:9\">2KI 2:9</a> <em>Elisha</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:9\">NEH 13:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:6-Isa6:7\">ISA 6:6–6:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:9\">JER 1:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:1\">EZK 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:23\">EZK 3:23</a></p>\n<h3>In the NT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:20-2Tim2:21\">2TI 2:20–2:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:19\">MAT 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:15\">LUK 1:15</a> <em>John the Baptist</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:41\">LUK 1:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:67\">LUK 1:67</a> <em>Zechariah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33\">LUK 12:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:8\">ACT 4:8</a> <em>Peter</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:3\">ACT 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:17\">ACT 9:17</a> <em>Ananias</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:24\">ACT 11:24</a> <em>Barnabas</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:12\">ROM 13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:12\">EPH 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11-Eph6:18\">EPH 6:11–6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:19\">PHP 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20-Heb13:21\">HEB 13:20–13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are equipped for spiritual tasks</h2>\n<h3>By the call of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:19\">MAT 4:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:17\">MRK 1:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:24-Mark10:31\">MRK 10:24–10:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1-Luke9:2\">LUK 9:1–9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:1-Luke10:3\">LUK 10:1–10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:35-John1:42\">JHN 1:35–1:42</a></p>\n<h3>By spiritual gifts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:7\">1CO 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:3-Acts6:6\">ACT 6:3–6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:6-Rom12:8\">ROM 12:6–12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:8-1Cor12:11\">1CO 12:8–12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:27-1Cor12:31\">1CO 12:27–12:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:7\">EPH 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11-Eph4:12\">EPH 4:11–4:12</a></p>\n<h3>By the word of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:15\">2TI 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">COL 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19\">2PE 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:14\">1JN 2:14</a></p>\n<h3>By the empowering of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:4\">ACT 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:9\">ACT 13:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18\">EPH 5:18</a></p>\n<h3>For spiritual conflict</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11\">EPH 6:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:12\">ROM 13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:20-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:20–4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:12-Eph6:18\">EPH 6:12–6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12-Col3:15\">COL 3:12–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:12\">1TI 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:21\">HEB 13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a></p>",
